rComments: THE best prof of uOttawa.  The only thing that you need to know is : This prof deserves a gold medal and she is not teaching anymore.  We had the chance to have her as a prof and uOttawa should really consider to try to make her come teaching again !  Merci France !
So excited to teach about math. Seems to really want you to like controls as much as she does. Really structured, clear communicator, one of the best ELG profs at ottawa u!
Final exam can be tough so try to do really well in midterm but She is good!!!

She is a very nice professor. Does lots of examples in class, and actually lets the students help do them! This helps the students learn the material much much faster. An excellent prof. I enjoyed her class the most.Reasonable exams, a bit long though.Fairly easy marking.Assignments aren't marked.Probably one of the best courses I have ever taken.
